  ('investigation-d4d4f144-moex-00079', 'investigation-d4d4f144', 'investigation-d4d4f144-moex-113-3f63b028', 'sub-investigation-d4d4f144-04', NULL, 'essay', '尚在大學就讀的甲，投資眼光精準，每日進出股市之金額動輒數千萬元，
