  ('investigation-d4d4f144-moex-00084', 'investigation-d4d4f144', 'investigation-d4d4f144-moex-113-8e4cfe31', 'sub-investigation-d4d4f144-05', NULL, 'essay', '一檔股票型基金的總市場價值為新臺幣 2,400 萬元，此基金持有涵蓋臺
